about.title: About me
about.text: I am determined and motivated, always eager to learn and grow. In my free time, I enjoy coding and exploring the latest technology, with a particular interest in software development. While studying, I developed my critical thinking, problem-solving, and teamwork skills through coursework and team projects. I often take on the role of team leader during collaborative projects. I am committed to improving my skills and knowledge and am excited to continue my career in software development.
